\pard \plain \cf0 \fs20
{\uldb Peter}{\v 20062}\par
\par
On entering the \b \i Peter - left \i0 \b0 command Peter will turn to the left by 90 degrees. The new orientation is rounded up to the next valid orientation value (according to the number of Peter sprite's orientation values). In case a preceding command to shift to a specified coordinate has been given he will first finish the shift before starting to turn.\par
